headline: Poland's PGE in preliminary agreement to buy assets from ZE PAK
summary: Poland's largest power producer PGE has struck a preliminary agreement to potentially buy gas-fired power plant project PAK CCGT from power plant operator ZE PAK, PGE said on Thursday. ...
